# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert
# Scopes: auth, layout, tree, document, comments, github, server, e2e, fixtures, skills, publish, docs, ci
#
# - imperative mood, lowercase, no trailing period
# - body: explain what and why (blank line after subject)
# - footer: BREAKING CHANGE: ..., Closes: ISSUE-123
